############################################################ # Body ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML An _anagram_ of a word is just a rearrangement of its letters. How many different anagrams of "uncopyrightable" are there? (This happens to be the longest common English word without any repeated letters.)
[_]{$ans}{5}
END_PGML
############################################################ # Solution ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION Since there are 15 different letters, we have 15 choices for the first letter, 14 for the next, and so on. Thus there are [`15!`] anagrams.
END_PGML_SOLUTION
