############################################################ # Body ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML On a business retreat, your company of 20 executives go golfing. a. You need to divide up into foursomes (groups of 4 people): a first foursome, a second foursome, and so on. How many ways can you do this?
[_]{$ans1}{10}
